des: "An easy and quick way to prepare eggplant, and tasty too!  I serve it with sliced fresh tomatoes, fresh green beans and bread and butter. An inexpensive meal from my childhood and still a favorite!"
ins: Heat oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.  Dip eggplant slices in egg, then in crumbs, and place in hot oil.  Fry 2 to 3 minutes on each side, or until golden brown.  Drain on paper towels.
